Gymshark Train
We train. We motivate. We grow. Together.
Step up your game and join the family, so we can #GymsharkTrain together 🦈

#Gymsharktrain

#Gymsharktrain

#Gymsharktrain

node.text:
Get ready to make that full body work with this powerful at-home HIIT workout from @mrandmrsmuscle 💪 
Tag a friend who you would duo this with!
#Gymsharktrain

Please only take part in the workout if you are medically and physically fit and have not been advised not to participate by a qualified medical professional. If your health or fitness changes adversely in any way before, during and/or after the workout please seek and follow medical advice without delay.

node.text:
@wozldn brings you a 🔥 full body workout to celebrate the last day of #Gymshark66! Expect 30 minutes of dynamic and energetic H.I.I.T exercises – you're defo going to need some water 🥵

Please only take part in the workout if you are medically and physically fit and have not been advised not to participate by a qualified medical professional. If your health or fitness changes adversely in any way before, during and/or after the workout please seek and follow medical advice without delay.

node.text:
Want to increase your flexibility? Then try this mobility flow routine by @jessicaolie 🙌
Click the link in our bio for more mobility workouts‼️ #Gymsharktrain

Set those quads and glutes on 🔥 with this hot workout!
Hit save and follow along with @whitneyysimmons:
1️⃣ Barbell front squats (4x8)
2️⃣ Front rack alternating lunge to squat (3x10)
3️⃣ Barbell hip thrusts (4x8)
4️⃣ Rear foot elevated split squat (3x10)
5️⃣ Landmine single leg hip thrusts (3x10)
#Gymsharktrain

ABS CIRCUIT 🔥
Run through the exercises as a circuit + repeat 3-4 times ⬇️
1️⃣ Single knee to chest (x12)
2️⃣ Straight leg raise (x10)
3️⃣ Oblique raise (x10)
4️⃣ Flutter kick (x40)
Tag a training partner you'll be trying this with.
📹: @nathan @megsutherland
#Gymsharktrain

If you're ready to make some serious change, give this focused @realrubaali workout a go!
💥 Dumbbell lunge
💥 Burpee with Star jump
💥 Leg raise with Overhead press
💥 Squat jump with Arnold press
💥 One-sided elevated push-up
12-15 reps per side | 4 sets | 30 sec rest after each set
Tag a friend to motivate their next workout 👇
#Gymsharktrain

Whether it's adding resistance, trying a new sport, or working out in a different location – switching up your routine could just be the secret to your success 💪
📹: @ericssonsamuel
#Gymsharktrain

node.text:
15 min HIIT workout you can do with your gym BFF 👭 💦
5 exercises | 30 sec on, 30 sec off | 3 rounds:
1️⃣ Lunge kick
2️⃣ Burpee to Tuck jump
3️⃣ Press up to Plank kick through
4️⃣ Star jumps with pause
5️⃣ Leg raise trio
Let's go!
📹: @demibagby 
#Gymsharktrain

node.text:
Throw these 3 exercises into your next back workout for the ultimate training session 🔥 💯
Follow along with @adotty10:
1️⃣ Head bangers/skull crushers (12x4)
2️⃣ Cable lat pulls (12x4)
3️⃣ Alt lat pull down (12x4)
#Gymsharktrain

If you love training with dumbbells, then this lower body workout is for you 🙌
Tap save and follow along with @hxhails:
✔️ Donkey kicks
✔️ Swing to Squat
✔️ Squat to Press
✔️ Dumbbell swings
✔️ Row to RDL
Perform each exercise for 20 reps + repeat circuit 4x.
#Gymsharktrain

#Gymsharktrain

node.text:
Try this if you have a busy schedule❗
If you're struggling to find time to workout, make this bodyweight HIIT your next session.
Workout details from @jahdy_p: Perform 30 sec on, 15 sec off for each exercise. Complete all exercises, take a 1 minute rest, then repeat 5x over.
💥 Knee + kick (R)
💥 Knee + kick (L)
💥 Explosive knees
💥 Plank combo
💥 One arm in/out combo
💥 180 degree jump kick
💥 Push-up shoulder tap
#Gymsharktrain
